<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Manoj K | Tech Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        /* Base styling and dark theme */
        body {
            background-color: #0d1117; /* Deep dark background */
            color: #c9d1d9; /* Light grey text */
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        /* Header section */
        header {
            background-color: #161b22;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #58a6ff; /* Developer blue */
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #3fb950; /* Terminal green */
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Main content container */
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        /* Individual sections */
        .section {
            background-color: #161b22;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #58a6ff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        /* Grid for projects */
        .project-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        @media (min-width: 600px) {
            .project-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }
        
        /* Individual project cards */
        .project-card {
            background-color: #0d1117;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
        }
        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            border-color: #58a6ff;
        }
        .project-title {
            color: #3fb950;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            border-top: 1px solid #30363d;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Manoj K</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">> Hardware Tinkerer | Security Enthusiast | AI Developer_</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Welcome to my workspace. I'm passionate about exploring the intersection of hardware and software. Whether it's building physical electronics, experimenting with Linux environments, or conceptualizing custom automation, I enjoy taking things apart to see how they work and building them back better.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Current Focus & Projects</h2>
            <div class="project-grid">
                
                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-title">🎙️ Custom Voice AI</div>
                    <p>Developing cloud-linked, persistent background AI agents using Python and Termux for hands-free automation and remote execution.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-title">⚙️ Hardware & Electronics</div>
                    <p>Working with ESP32 microcontrollers, custom motherboard wiring, mechanical systems, and automated sensor networks.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-title">🔐 Security Studies</div>
                    <p>Exploring network security tools, OSINT frameworks, and ethical hacking concepts utilizing Kali NetHunter and terminal environments.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-title">💻 Technical Tutorials</div>
                    <p>Documenting my builds, code, and troubleshooting processes to eventually share knowledge through tech tutorials and guides.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Built with HTML/CSS | Hosted free on GitHub Pages</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
